<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Distribution map of P. aurea (Klug), P. binghami Bischoff, P. dhofarensis sp. nov., and P. maura Bischoff in the Arabian Peninsula." , "Figure 26. Pseudophotopsis maura Bischoff (Female) A, B habitus, lateral and dorsal views, respectively." , "Figure 27. Pseudophotopsis maura Bischoff (Female) A head, frontal view B head and antennal scape, dorsal view C antenna D mesosoma, dorsal view E head and mesosoma, lateral view." , "Figure 25. Pseudophotopsis maura Bischoff (Male) A metasoma, dorsal view B 1 st and 2 nd metasomal segments latero-ventral view (median basal tubercle on S 2 indicated)." , "Figure 24. Pseudophotopsis maura Bischoff (Male) A head, lateral view B antenna C mesosoma, dorsal view D right fore wing." , "Figure 34. Male genitalia A, B Pseudophotopsis mascatiana Invrea, dorsal and ventral views, respectively C, D P. maura Bischoff, dorsal and ventral views, respectively." , "Figure 23. Pseudophotopsis maura Bischoff (Male) A, B habitus, lateral and dorsal views, respectively C, D head, frontal and dorsal views, respectively." , "Figure 28. Pseudophotopsis maura Bischoff (Female) A T 1 and T 2, dorsal view B T 3 - T 6, dorsal view C T 6 (showing pygidial area) D metasoma, lateral view (median basal tubercle on S 2 indicated)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537904" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537907" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537908" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537882" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537915" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537905" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537906" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/537909" .

